title: Alix_Senator_The_Eagles_of_Blood_(2012) (Dragonz-Onairam-Choky-T
description:
Rome,12BC the Emperor Augustus is all powerful.Alix is more than 50 years old.He is also a senator.
Peace finally seems to prevail throughout the empire.Agrippa,the son-in-law of Augustus,is brutally killed by an eagle,the bird of jupiter!Whether this is a political attack or a divine curse,it is up to alix to discover what lies behaind the mysterious death.
